have written the same thing, that truth
is truth, and truth is love.

00:30:35.350 --> 00:30:38.560
That’s what Christ wanted to establish,

00:30:38.761 --> 00:30:43.596
but He was born in a very, very difficult
situation.

00:30:43.797 --> 00:30:49.238
And the people who took over, as priests
and Church and all that,

00:30:49.439 --> 00:30:56.482
made full advantage of that and have really
oppressed all the people.

00:30:56.762 --> 00:31:02.784
There’s no oppression in Sahaja Yoga.
It’s your free will by which you come in.

00:31:02.985 --> 00:31:09.854
And you have to find the truth, truth about
yourself, you should know yourself.

00:31:10.055 --> 00:31:13.659
All the time Christ has said, “Know
Thyself.”

00:31:13.860 --> 00:31:16.847
And they don’t try that at all anywhere,
Knowing Thyself,

00:31:17.048 --> 00:31:20.523
because they don’t know themselves.

00:31:22.422 --> 00:31:28.781
This situation we have in every religion.

00:31:28.982 --> 00:31:36.493
They all came to fight it, to tell us
what is the right path what to follow.

00:31:36.694 --> 00:31:39.855
What Christ did was a very remarkable
thing,

00:31:40.056 --> 00:31:47.293
that He told the Jews that He is the Light,
He is the Path.

00:31:47.499 --> 00:31:50.897
But He didn’t say He was the destination,
clearly,

00:31:51.098 --> 00:31:55.585
because He knew that somebody has to come,

00:31:55.786 --> 00:32:00.454
and He said the Holy Ghost will come,

00:32:00.655 --> 00:32:03.934
and She’ll have three things as you know:

00:32:04.135 --> 00:32:10.657
that She’ll be a Comforter, She’ll be
a Counselor, and She’ll be a Redeemer.

00:32:10.858 --> 00:32:17.732
He didn’t use She or He, but in Hebrew
language it says “It”.

00:32:18.364 --> 00:32:23.519
So people have misused Bible to such
an extent that in England

00:32:23.720 --> 00:32:29.102
a king wanted to divorce his wife so he
authorized the Bible.

00:32:29.303 --> 00:32:35.599
How can such an adharmic fellow authorize
such a holy book like Bible?

00:32:35.835 --> 00:32:41.546
Because the power: with the power he want
to control,

00:32:41.746 --> 00:32:47.029
want to control all that is reality.

00:32:47.230 --> 00:32:49.819
This is a blind power.

00:32:50.020 --> 00:32:55.675
But if you have a real power, then you know
what to respect, what not to respect.

00:32:55.876 --> 00:32:58.015
Which way to go, which way not to go.

00:32:58.216 --> 00:33:06.070
Because you have a sight, you know a very
bright understanding of the whole thing.

00:33:06.271 --> 00:33:13.581
Which road you have to follow, where you
have to go, and which is the right thing.

00:33:13.782 --> 00:33:19.295
Thank God through this Kali Yuga, because
of all kinds of horrible things,

00:33:19.496 --> 00:33:24.863
as also among Hindus lots of funny, funny
rituals they have,

00:33:25.064 --> 00:33:31.852
that people have seen through that this is
not the end of it.

00:33:32.053 --> 00:33:35.595
You have to seek, you have to seek.

00:33:35.812 --> 00:33:41.628
But the only thing which is very important
is that all of them have said

00:33:41.829 --> 00:33:46.154
that you have to seek, you have to find out
your Self.

00:33:46.355 --> 00:33:51.272
Which is very clearly written in some
of the Indian scriptures.

00:33:51.473 --> 00:33:54.370
Some of them, I would say not all of them.

00:33:54.571 --> 00:33:57.771
Some of them it is written that you must
seek your Self,

00:33:57.972 --> 00:34:02.767
specially the saints who came on this earth
in India,

00:34:02.968 --> 00:34:09.161
they have tried to say all the time that
you must seek,

00:34:09.362 --> 00:34:12.829
you must find out the truth. Because they
knew the truth

00:34:13.030 --> 00:34:16.028
and they wanted others to find the truth.

00:34:16.229 --> 00:34:20.109
So in every religion there have been
enlightened people.

00:34:20.310 --> 00:34:27.075
Among Buddhists also there has been
a Viditama, Lao-Tse, and many others,

00:34:27.276 --> 00:34:32.715
who have talked about seeking, seeking
the truth.

00:34:32.917 --> 00:34:37.081
Christ has said it very clearly, very, very
clearly,

00:34:37.282 --> 00:34:44.267
and at His birthday I feel very happy that
so many of you

00:34:44.468 --> 00:34:48.243
have already found out the truth and that
you know

00:34:48.444 --> 00:34:52.961
the path of love and compassion and
humility.

00:34:53.162 --> 00:34:58.006
As it is we know where Christ resides
within us,

00:34:58.207 --> 00:35:02.453
and how to respect Christ, and how
to worship it.

00:35:02.654 --> 00:35:06.223
With this Agnya chakra you can make out
a person

00:35:06.424 --> 00:35:15.070
whether he is a seeker or he is
a dominating arrogant Christian.

00:35:16.144 --> 00:35:19.794
You cannot do that, if you are a Christian
you cannot be that.

00:35:19.995 --> 00:35:22.646
If you are that, then you are not
a Christian.

00:35:22.847 --> 00:35:25.499
Look at Christ, how humble He was.

00:35:25.700 --> 00:35:30.458
He could have finished them off - He had
such powers - all of them;

00:35:30.659 --> 00:35:38.358
but He got Himself crucified. The reason
was Agnya chakra was to be broken.

00:35:38.559 --> 00:35:42.120
Was to be crossed. And so He accepted.

00:35:42.321 --> 00:35:45.420
As I told you He had all the powers
of Shri Ganesha,

00:35:45.621 --> 00:35:52.463
which are the most destructive powers.

00:35:52.664 --> 00:35:57.270
All these powers come from Mother Earth,

00:35:57.471 --> 00:36:01.814
and the Mother Earth can shake the whole
world.

00:36:02.015 --> 00:36:06.327
But He was the One who came as Mahavishnu,

00:36:06.515 --> 00:36:11.552
as described in the Devi Mahatmya. What
a person He was,

00:36:11.753 --> 00:36:16.354
and what He did, all His work is
beautifully described in Mahavishnu.

00:36:17.206 --> 00:36:24.088
Now, when they do not know, want to connect the Devi Mahatmya with Christ’s work,

00:36:24.526 --> 00:36:28.002
it’s alright, they are lost.

00:36:28.065 --> 00:36:32.776
There’s such a disintegration, and there’s no collectivity, nothing.

00:36:33.018 --> 00:36:39.226
And they call themselves as the disciples of Christ: you cannot.

00:36:39.813 --> 00:36:42.321
You must have love, compassion.

00:36:42.462 --> 00:36:47.290
And not for a purpose. They have missionaries who go and

00:36:47.446 --> 00:36:53.897
talk of compassion, love, and what they achieve is nothing but conversion, because

00:36:53.929 --> 00:36:57.765
it is democracy and they want to have more heads.

00:36:57.845 --> 00:37:03.185
It’s so despising, the whole attitude towards Christ,

00:37:03.326 --> 00:37:08.505
is so criminal to have such an attitude towards Christ,

00:37:08.584 --> 00:37:12.754
who was the One who came to give salvation to the whole world,

00:37:13.285 --> 00:37:18.902
to unite the whole world, and to make so many different, different

00:37:18.926 --> 00:37:22.652
efforts to spoil His name.

00:37:23.082 --> 00:37:30.322
Now I would tell you this, that if Christ
is born and He came on this earth,

00:37:30.523 --> 00:37:33.150
it’s a very, very great occasion.

00:37:33.351 --> 00:37:36.469
He gave His life for us, He did everything.

00:37:36.670 --> 00:37:41.250
And how are we following Him is
by forgiving.

00:37:41.451 --> 00:37:47.193
You have to forgive others, you forgive
yourself and you forgive others.

00:37:47.394 --> 00:37:51.491
Is very important if you want to open this
Agnya chakra,

00:37:51.692 --> 00:37:56.203
where resides our Lord Jesus Christ.

00:37:56.404 --> 00:37:59.715
If you cannot forgive others

00:37:59.916 --> 00:38:04.892
and you cannot forgive yourself, then this
Agnya won’t open.

00:38:05.093 --> 00:38:09.747
And the best part of it, all the Christian
nations I have seen,

00:38:09.956 --> 00:38:15.811
where there are so-called Christians, they
all have a very bad Agnya.

00:38:16.012 --> 00:38:21.650
If they are really following Christ, why
should there be a catch on the Agnya chakra?

00:38:21.851 --> 00:38:29.169
And they are extremely dominating, arrogant
people.

00:38:29.528 --> 00:38:35.357
They cannot be the disciples of Christ.
He was so humble,

00:38:35.558 --> 00:38:43.294
He was so much one with God Almighty, that
He accepted His crucifixion.

00:38:43.495 --> 00:38:48.492
His birth itself is a very great miracle,

00:38:48.693 --> 00:38:51.729
and His work is even greater.

00:38:51.930 --> 00:38:58.142
We have to win over all the Christians and
tell them what is real Christianity,

00:38:58.343 --> 00:39:01.983
what is reality, and what they should
take to,

00:39:02.184 --> 00:39:07.335
and how they should justify their following
of Christ.

00:39:07.536 --> 00:39:14.328
It is very big organizational thing, and
it’s a big, I mean, political thing,

00:39:14.529 --> 00:39:20.586
I mean, all kinds of things are going on.
And all the bad things they have

00:39:20.787 --> 00:39:25.110
from, say Hindu religion, they carry on.

00:39:25.333 --> 00:39:29.083
So what is the use of conversion also?

00:39:29.284 --> 00:39:36.598
So from His life we have to learn that
He took a birth

00:39:36.885 --> 00:39:44.138
in such a situation that nobody would have
dared to be born like that.

00:39:44.339 --> 00:39:49.962
So much of darkness and ignorance, so much
of cruelty,

00:39:50.163 --> 00:39:55.134
that He took His birth at that time is
extremely remarkable.

00:39:55.335 --> 00:39:58.962
Such a brave, courageous personality.

00:39:59.186 --> 00:40:02.666
Nowadays they make Christ look like
a TB patient, I mean,

00:40:02.867 --> 00:40:09.671
just to beg, you know. Because they are
beggars. All the time they are begging.

00:40:09.872 --> 00:40:16.385
And I was in Bombay this time, some little,
little girls and boys were singing songs

00:40:16.586 --> 00:40:20.479
and they came up, and they said, “Give us
some money.”

00:40:20.680 --> 00:40:23.236
I said, “What are you doing?”
“We are singing carols.”

00:40:23.437 --> 00:40:26.413
“So you sing! Why do you need money for?”

00:40:26.614 --> 00:40:31.568
“You know, we need money, we have no food
to eat.” Imagine.

00:40:31.769 --> 00:40:37.147
Then why sing songs of Christ?

00:40:38.038 --> 00:40:44.896
All kinds of begging is done. Christ, did
He beg for anything?

00:40:45.097 --> 00:40:48.785
Did He want to create beggars on this
earth?

00:40:48.986 --> 00:40:54.212
He died, lived with self-respect.

00:40:54.413 --> 00:40:59.296
All His qualities are never studied and
people take

00:40:59.497 --> 00:41:08.594
to something which is very mundane,
sometimes absolutely degrading, degrading.

00:41:08.795 --> 00:41:14.462
He came to give us a very dharmic,

00:41:14.671 --> 00:41:19.681
very… I shouldn’t say religious because
that's different meaning,

00:41:19.882 --> 00:41:25.817
but I would say a very pious and beautiful
life.

00:41:26.018 --> 00:41:30.019
He is the model, He is the model we have
to follow.

00:41:30.596 --> 00:41:35.486
Not that to become beggars and go round and ask for alms.

00:41:35.987 --> 00:41:41.338
Even in the schools which are Christian schools they teach this to children, that

00:41:41.542 --> 00:41:44.291
you go and ask for money, ask for money;

00:41:44.316 --> 00:41:46.705
all over the world they are asking for money.

00:41:46.792 --> 00:41:49.705
And what do they do with their money God only knows.

00:41:49.768 --> 00:41:55.486
Money can never be so important, never so important

00:41:55.750 --> 00:42:03.272
– it is just that we use it, but it cannot dominate us.

00:42:05.499 --> 00:42:10.132
He came in a very, very humble way, in a manger He was born,

00:42:10.320 --> 00:42:12.786
to show that money is not important.

00:42:14.468 --> 00:42:24.530
Though in the Sanskrit literature it is written that a God, or God Almighty when He incarnates,

00:42:24.843 --> 00:42:32.843
He has aishwarya, means He has wealth,
He must have wealth.

00:42:33.941 --> 00:42:37.433
It is meaning the spiritual wealth.

00:42:37.472 --> 00:42:40.972
He must be born with the spiritual wealth.

00:42:41.190 --> 00:42:46.730
If he has spiritual wealth, then He is the real incarnation.

00:42:47.347 --> 00:42:51.626
If you don’t have the spiritual wealth of love and compassion,

00:42:52.057 --> 00:42:57.275
and detachment, you cannot be called as an incarnation.

00:42:57.432 --> 00:43:04.275
It’s a myth. So we have to test it on people who are saying they are incarnations,

00:43:04.299 --> 00:43:08.470
they are gods, they are divine, that they will take you to divine life.

00:43:08.494 --> 00:43:11.009
See their own lives, how they live.

00:43:12.221 --> 00:43:14.361
See their own temperament.

00:43:15.873 --> 00:43:18.615
You can see how Christ knew about:

00:43:18.680 --> 00:43:23.107
He told Peter that you’ll meet a satan.

00:43:23.522 --> 00:43:25.922
And that’s what he met, this Paul.

00:43:26.827 --> 00:43:36.122
In every incarnation’s life there has been negative force curbing the activity of that incarnation.

00:43:36.560 --> 00:43:42.364
We too had lots of negative forces, but gradually we have surmounted it

00:43:42.458 --> 00:43:49.348
and still I am there living, it’s no, there’s no crucifixion for Me at least.

00:43:50.200 --> 00:43:58.200
So this is what it is, because you are seekers and you have found the truth.

00:43:59.263 --> 00:44:04.614
This was My job, is to give you the truth. And you have got it,

00:44:04.817 --> 00:44:10.395
you have got the spiritual experience, which is the greatest thing one can ask for.

00:44:10.692 --> 00:44:14.792
You know yourself and you are so one with each other.

00:44:15.035 --> 00:44:20.923
This is the completion of the work of Christ, that He said ‘I will send you the Holy Ghost’.

00:44:21.457 --> 00:44:27.729
