That’s why Christ came on this world to show, and they put all these things on Him, and take a license to do whatever they like.

00:48:40.992 --> 00:48:46.261
After Sahaja Yoga you realize what is
wrong, what is good.

00:48:46.462 --> 00:48:54.254
Unless and until you become a sahaja yogi
is difficult to have this discrimination.

00:48:54.455 --> 00:48:58.300
That’s how so many people are lost
in the name of Christ,

00:48:58.501 --> 00:49:04.956
lost in the destructive forces of their
being.

00:49:05.157 --> 00:49:13.799
As it is we call them all the six enemies
that we have.

